claim.claim-text:
18. A component of an e-cigarette, the component comprising a housing holding a liquid, the housing comprising:
a liquid reservoir holding the liquid;
a wick to take up the liquid; and
a heater for heating the wick;
wherein the liquid reservoir is provided with a liquid outlet configured to supply liquid to the wick and an air duct to create an air flow along the wick and to an air outlet, and
wherein the heater and the wick are combined to form a combined construction located between a first support member and an opposite second support member to hold the combined construction in a fixed position.
